_info_examples.iso_639_3_eng:
```json
{
    "my_number": {
        "_rule_selection-values_one": [1, 2, 3],
        "_rule_selection-values_any": [4, 5],
        "_rule_selection-values_all": [10, 20]
    },
    "my_label": {
        "_rule_selection-values_one": ["default label"]
    }
}
```

This will set:

- `my_number` to one of `1`, `2` or `3`; any of `4` or/and `5`, and both `10` and `20`.
- `my_label` to `"default label"`.
